{
 "file": "_STGSP6B.bin",
 "source_size": 36288,
 "built_size": 38712,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17fa",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "马上就要抵达地球轨道了",
   "zh_hex": "15e84fb2e7c5ef2ae96eef2bbf95e9cce82ae7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x182d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到目前为止还算顺利……正规军已经到了{00}吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7d5bae7c1e869e7f7e889eab4e82e0909ef3bea42e7e0ef3ae8b7e7d7e7ba00e802050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1864",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球轨道舰队似乎正在待命、准备与我们{00}会合",
   "zh_hex": "15bf95e9cce82ae7d4e7c9e944e933ef3bef29eaa8e85302e87ae877e8328be7bb00e7e2a000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1899",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就这样与轨道舰队会合……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5e7b9e7dae832e9cce82ae7d4e7c9e7e2a0090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1922",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！这、这是攻击！？到底是从哪儿打来{00}的！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b902e7b9e7b6ef67e7ccef9705e7d7e9b4e7b6e88ae8ffeb7ce7f5efcf00e7b4ef97050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x195d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请稍等！现在……",
   "zh_hex": "15e83aead5e826ef97e82fef290909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c0",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……拉米亚斯舰长！！刚才那波攻击、你{00}注意到了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34ef97ef97e8bce836e7b7e9a8ef67e7cc02e7b800eaccef3ce7d7e7bae802ef97050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19f4",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf305000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a16",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "攻击是从我们正前方打来的！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef67e7cce7b6e88aefcce7bbef3bef51efb1e7f5efcfe7b4ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a28",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟是地球轨道舰队打来的炮击！{00}这……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7b6bf95e9cce82ae7d4e7c9e7f5d9e7b4e95ae7cc0600e7b9090906060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a5a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bd0909ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a79",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "立刻停船！大天使号！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86be91fe934ea02ef97efa5e844e83fe833ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab1",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球轨道舰队……{00}难道说、真的是他们……？",
   "zh_hex": "15bf95e9cce82ae7d4e7c9090900e866e82ae7ed02e820e7b4e7b6e80ce7bb090905000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ae1",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b0f",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰队司令！这到底是怎么回事！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4e7c9eafee94eef97e7b9e7d7e9b4e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb8ef97050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b3f",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你还问『怎么回事』？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f7e9970ce7f2e7bdef52efb80d0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b4d",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……少跟我装糊涂！",
   "zh_hex": "150909eface973efcce98feda0ee53ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b59",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们背叛地球联邦、{00}早已是明摆着的事实！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe9e4ef43bf95ef2ed10200e963ef3ae7b6ef39eb8be86de7b4a9e87f0600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b90",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bd0909ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bbd",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们勾结海盗、袭击了我们的运输船……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbecb7e868e91be9f302e9aee7cce7baefcce7bbe7b4e986e8b9ea0209090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bdb",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……难道不是吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e866e82ae7b5e7b6e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c05",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef69e8f8efc40909ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c2b",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "帝国？你在说什么呢？我们可是木星公社{00}的人",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f8efc405e7b8ef29e7ede7dde7bde90705efcce7bbe7c4e7b6efa9ef69e9a4ed9600e7b4efb200000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c4a",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "说什么木星有帝国……{00}这种毫无根据的中伤、还请你省省吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ede7dde7bdd4b5e7cbe8f8a1090900e7b9e7d1ea0ae7dce9b8e8cce7b4c0e8f902e7f7e83ae7b8ecf4ecf4e7d000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c93",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贵队的越轨行径、经木星公社通报、早已{00}一清二楚",
   "zh_hex": "15e930e7c9e7b4ea57e9ccefd6ecd302e8b7efa9ef69e9a4ed96ef59e91302e963ef3a00efb6e995ea13ebd30000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cb2",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对作为地球生命线的木星船团发动攻击、{00}就等同于背叛联邦！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef2fe7c1ef63efd3ef8de853e916e7b4efa9ef69ea02ea5ee870ef30ef67e7cc0200e7c5e826e85de879e9e4ef43ef2eefaaef970000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cf6",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……请你们等一下！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e83ae7b8e7bbe826efb6ef4def97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d04",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "关于木星帝国的存在、我们早就提交过报{00}告……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bbe879efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7b4e993ef2902efcce7bbe963e7c5e821e861ef36e91300e8e50909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d38",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "都说了、根本就没有什么木星帝国！",
   "zh_hex": "15e840e7ede7ba02e9b8efa6e7c5e7d8e7cbe7dde7bdefa9ef69e8f8efc4ef9700000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d59",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明摆着的、只有随你们同行的十字先锋成{00}员、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39eb8be86de7b402ef32e7cbe9a1e7b8e7bbe85defd6e7b4ea4ae980ef8be967e83700e8490200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d78",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "频繁袭击公社运输船、这才是唯一的事实{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eec6eda1e9aee7cce9a4ed96e986e8b9ea0202e7b9e836e7b6ea89efb6e7b4efb8e87f00ef97ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d9b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "立刻投降便罢！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86be91fe948e943e8faeaefef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dad",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "否则、就当贵队发动了叛乱、即刻开始攻{00}击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9bbea8702e7c5ef53e930e7c9e870ef30e7baef43e97602e855e91fe7fae908ef6700e7ccef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1df3",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没想到、木星帝国的手、竟已伸进了军方{00}内部……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7e6e7d702efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7b4ef6602ef2cef3aedd7e892e7bae7e0efb100e99aef700909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e33",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e61",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e6a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下、我们又要被军方追着跑了呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4d02efcce7bbe8f1ef2ae7f1e7e0efb1e8dde86deb6fe7bae90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e9a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉米亚斯舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef340000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ea1",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "趁后续部队还没赶来、我们先撤退吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e9eae7fee9adef70e7c9e7f7e7d8ea04efcf02efcce7bbef8be90ae880e7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ed8",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、说得也是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502e7ede80ae7c0e7b6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f23",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS部队、立刻归舰！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7ef9eef70e7c902e86be91fe947e7d4ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f31",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "预防者全舰、即刻撤退！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea5ae968ef6eefb4e7d402e855e91fe90ae880ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f66",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之、对方似乎还没派出追击部队",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd02e7beefb1e944e933e7f7e7d8e985efbee8dde7ccef70e7c90000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f99",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fa0",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "话说回来、{00}没想到又要被军方追着跑了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81fe7ed8cd90200e7d8e7e6e7d7e8f1ef2ae7f1e7e0d0e8dde86deb6fe7ba090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fbe",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们、是不是被什么给诅咒了呢",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bb02e7b6e7b5e7b6e7f1e7dde7bde839ec93ec52e7bae90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fed",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、是不是被诅咒、就先不说了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e7b6e7b5e7b6e7f1ec93ec5202e7c5ef8be7b5e7ede7ba090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2004",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "局势确实变棘手了",
   "zh_hex": "15ea8ce8fde88ce87fe955ed79ef66e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2032",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国……是吗",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef69e8f8efc40909e7b6e80200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2057",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "军方那帮人已被他们拉拢、毫无危机意识",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e0efb1e7b7e910efb2ef3ae7f1e80ce7bbe7c2ed6502ea0ae7dce935e7e4ef3ce92f000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2094",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而且、刚才那一战、还给了他们进军地球{00}圈的借口",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce99902e8bce836e7b7efb6ef2802e7f7e839e7bae80ce7bbe892e7e0ef63efd300e9fbe7b4eadceabd00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20bb",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若木星帝国当真露出獠牙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7efa9ef69e8f8efc4ef53e820e858efbeececebd709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20f7",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那联邦军怕是会一触即溃吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ef2eefaae7e0e958e7b6e7e2efb6ef48e855ec79e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x212d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2136",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我父亲他",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce888e894e80c000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x213e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我父亲曾说过、地球这种东西、他根本不{00}需要",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce888e894ea2ae7edef3602ef63efd3e7b9e7d1e8bae7f802e80ce9b8efa6e7b500e92def2a00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2173",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……地球？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef63efd3050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x217c",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道说、杜加奇是想毁掉整个地球……",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82ae7ed02e8cbe854e904e7b6e7e6e97ce9d3e9fee828bf95090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21ad",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这也并非不可能",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e7c0e957e8f0e7b5e7c4e7c60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21c7",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不！若是杜加奇、他一定会那么做！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b506e7e7e7b6e8cbe854e90402e80c87e867e7e2e7b7e7bde81c06060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21f5",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用无数生命才好不容易换来的、如今这份{00}和平……",
   "zh_hex": "15d8e7dce914b6e853e836e7c7e7b5ed2fe964ea78d9e7b402e7f0a2e7b9ea2200e7d3e88709090000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x220f",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕它只是转瞬即逝、我们也必须守住它",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958e978ef32e7b6e9c2ebdfe855ec9d02efcce7bbe7c0e860e9a2e8a8e859e9780000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2255",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x225c",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "决不能让这个正走向和平的世界、重新陷{00}入战乱",
   "zh_hex": "15e8abe7b5e7c6e7f9e7b9e828ef3be890efc1e7d3e887e7b4e83ce8f502e8a1ef8aeaf900e891ef28e976000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22a2",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若木星帝国当真要毁灭地球、那无论如何{00}都得阻止它！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7efa9ef69e8f8efc4ef53e820ef2ae97ce8e1ef63efd302e7b7e7dce8dce7f0efbc00e840e80ae8efe869e978ef970000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22e8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、说得对",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7ede80ae7be00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22f1",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕只剩我们、也只能拼了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958ef32ea3aefcce7bb02e7c0ef32e7c6ea66e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x231d",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "照刚才贝尔纳黛特说的来看、",
   "zh_hex": "15ea1ae8bce836e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfe7ede7b4efcfe7f6020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2330",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杜加奇的目标、恐怕就是地球本身",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cbe854e904e7b4d5e96f02eb33e958e7c5e7b6bf95d2e88d000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2349",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要打过去、把木星帝国军的大本营端掉{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7f5ef36e7eb02e81befa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e0e7b4efa5efa6ed01eab1e9d30009090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2380",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国、是被格拉克斯·杜加奇严密掌{00}控的国家！",
   "zh_hex": "15d4b5e8f8a102e7b6e7f1e824e7c2e7d5e7c804e8cbe854e904eaa1e9bdeb3600ea3fe7b4a1e7df0600000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x239e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要打倒杜加奇、木星帝国就会土崩瓦解{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7f5e848e8cbe854e90402d4b5e8f8a1e7c5e7e2ec56ebc2e99fe89d0006060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23d0",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "胜机、我已经看到了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8dbe7e402efccef3ae8b7e7f6e7d7e7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ea",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各舰、立刻做好出击准备！",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d402e86be91fe81ce7c7efbee7cce87ae877ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23fd",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "等准备一就绪、我们就向木星帝国军发起{00}决战！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e826e87ae877efb6e7c5efee02efcce7bbe7c5efc1efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e0e870e84700e8abef28ef97ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d52",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么、竟要在这里败下阵来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bd02ef2cef2aef29e7b9ef31e88fef4deb48efcf0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fd6",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7002",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……扎比涅！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e84be825eacf0605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7032",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诸位、是地球轨道舰队的吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15ea56e83402e7b6bf95e9cce82ae7d4e7c9e7b4e7d005000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7044",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们奉杜加奇阁下之命、{00}特来支援贵队！！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7bbeac1e8cbe854e904e8d789e7cde8530200e7cfd9e883e863e930e7c906060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7081",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦哦、是木星的诸位啊！！多谢相助！",
   "zh_hex": "15e919e91902e7b6efa9ef69e7b4ea56e834e7c3ef97ef97e7e9e8b2e8b1ea23ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70db",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（呵呵……扎比涅·夏尔……干得漂亮）",
   "zh_hex": "150aef3def3d0909e84be825eacf04ef37e7e10909e8d3e80aead0eaa20b0000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70f3",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（这下、要让大军开进地球圈、就更容易{00}了……）",
   "zh_hex": "150ae7b98902ef2ae7f9bee7e0e7fae892bf95e9fb02e7c5e952ed2fe96400e7ba09090b00000000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7118",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！MS队、出击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97efa7ef9ee7c902efbee7ccef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7127",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与联邦军联手、把那帮海盗一举击溃！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e832ef2eefaae7e0ef2eef6602e81be7b7e910e91be9f3efb6ea21e7ccec79ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7166",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7175",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道是……贝尔纳黛特！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82ae7b60909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf0605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x719d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d60909060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71c1",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "果然是你、贝尔纳黛特！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e871e7efe7b6e7b802e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71cd",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你怎么会在这里……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f2e7bde7e2ef29e7b9ef310909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71f3",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不行、托比亚！快逃！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b59f02e7f4e825e7d606e85fe8c206060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x721e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝尔纳黛特！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7242",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不行啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5efd6e7c3ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x724a",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这台机体不是我在开、{00}是电脑在操控它……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ea16e7e4bce7b5e7b68bef29e7fa0200e7b6ead3eb67ef29eac7ea3fe978090906000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7263",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我根本拦不住它！{00}所以快逃啊、托比亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "158be9b8d2eb89e7b5e859e9780600e7fbe7f3e85fe8c2e7c302e7f4e825e7d6060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7298",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！杜加奇！！竟然对亲生女儿做出这{00}种事！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de06e8cbe854e9040606ef2ce7efe7bee894b6b0eb7ce81cafe7b900e7d1a906000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72cd",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d6090906000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72f0",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别怕、贝尔纳黛特！！我马上……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e95802e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97ef97efcce84fef4c0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7307",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "立刻把你从那里面救出来！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86be91fe81be7b8e88ae7b7ef31e862e8caefbeefcfef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x733e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是什么……！？那台机动装甲……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7dde7bd0909ef9705e7b7ea16e7e4ef30e98febdb09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7351",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "里面不是贝尔纳黛特、我感觉到了另一股{00}气息！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef31e862e7b5e7b6e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf02efcce87de8aee7d7e7bae99befb6edac00e8edec6aef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x736a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是谁！是谁在那里面！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e923ef97e7b6e923ef29e7b7ef31e862ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73af",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呼哈哈哈哈！好眼力啊、臭小子！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea3ce7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97e7c7e90befb0e7c302ecfde83ee886ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73ed",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这个声音……！？是父亲大人！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e828ea8aea710909ef9705e7b6e888e894efa5efb2ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x741f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "格拉克斯·杜加奇……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e824e7c2e7d5e7c804e8cbe854e9040909060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x745d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没错、臭小子",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e88502ecfde83ee886000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x746a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "操控这台机体的、正是格拉克斯·杜加奇{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15eac7ea3fe7b9ea16e7e4bce7b402ef3be7b6e824e7c2e7d5e7c804e8cbe854e90400090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7482",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是把他的思维模式转写而成的生体头脑",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e81be80ce7b4efcaea54ea91ea26e9c2ede3e89ce837e7b4ef8def4fe92eeb67000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7496",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可就算你看穿了、又能怎样呢、臭小子？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7c5e889e7b8e7f6ea7ee7ba02e8f1e7c6e7f2e7dae90702ecfde83ee88605000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74d5",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你说什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7ede7dde7bdef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7511",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你拼命想救的那个女孩、正握在我手心里",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ea66e853e7e6e8cae7b4e7b7e828efade95602ef3beb37ef29efccef66e82def310000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x752a",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你还下得了手吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f7ef4de80ae7baef66e802ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x755b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那可是你的亲生女儿啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c4e7b6e7b8e7b4e894ef8defadeb7ce7c3ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x756d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是人说得出口的话吗！你这混蛋——！{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6efb2e7ede80aefbeeabde7b4e81fe802ef97e7b8e7b9ea41ea6debafebafef9700ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75b7",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈哈、可笑至极！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e802e7c4ea1ce897eacaef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75c6",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战斗哪分什么卑劣与高尚！这可是战争啊{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ffe8ffefaee7dde7bdec4bec0de832e812ecceef97e7b9e7c4e7b6ef28e852e7c300ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7609",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杜加奇……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cbe854e9040909060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x763a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战争……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e8520909ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x764f",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "格拉克斯·杜加奇！不管你怎么想……",
   "zh_hex": "15e824e7c2e7d5e7c804e8cbe854e90406e7b5e93be7b8e7f2e7bde7e60909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7671",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我可不是在跟你打什么战争！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c4e7b5e7b6ef29e973e7b8e7f5e7dde7bdef28e852ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x768a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝尔纳黛特、我要夺回来！",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf02efccef2aea17ef52efcfef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76c2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就是现在！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e7b6e82fef29ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76ee",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我一定要把贝尔纳黛特夺回来！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefb6e867ef2ae81be857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfea17ef52efcfef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7732",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！这臭小子！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b9ecfde83ee886ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x776e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她可不是属于你的东西！",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ee7c4e7b5e7b6ea24e879e7b8e7b4e8bae7f8ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77ae",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就照我们海盗的作风……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5ea1aefcce7bbe91be9f3e7b4ef2feb750909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77ee",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我就把她笑纳了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c5e81be88eea1ce882e7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x782a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d606060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7856",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "已经没事了、贝尔纳黛特……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3ae8b7e7d8efb8e7ba02e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x788b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯！……嗯！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e865ef970909e865ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78be",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78e2",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托比亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e825e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7904",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、贝尔纳黛特？睡不着吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf05ebdee7b5e86de80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7936",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我在想一些事情……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef29e7e6efb6e8a4efb8e88b09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7945",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7969",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……贝尔纳黛特？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x798e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我父亲他……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce888e894e80c0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7996",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我总觉得、父亲他、其实早就已经死{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce881e8aee80a02e888e894e80c02e8cfe87fe963e7c5ef3ae8b7ef6a00e7ba000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79b3",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以如今对木星军下令的、是父亲的复制{00}人格！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3e7f0a2e7bed4b5e7e089e94ee7b402e7b6e888e894e7b4e9eee8de00b4e82406000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79d2",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "否则、他绝不会做出那么残忍的事……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9bbea8702e80ce91ce7b5e7e2e81cefbee7b7e7bde97beb59e7b4efb80909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a05",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝尔纳黛特……",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a29",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "听我说、托比亚！所以……所以……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d18be7ed02e7f4e825e7d606e7fbe7f30909e7fbe7f30909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a3e",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以快阻止他！求你阻止他吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3e85fe8efe869e80cef97e93ae7b8e8efe869e80ce7d0ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a50",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别再让父亲的执念、{00}做出更残忍的事了！！",
